-- Russian FinMin places $2.1 bln at 28-day deposit auction
-- By Elena Fabrichnaya and Lidia Kelly
-- Mon Nov 17, 2014 04:34AM EST
-- None



MOSCOW, Nov 17 (Reuters) - The Russian Finance Ministry said on Monday it had placed $2.1 billion at a 28-day deposit auction at rate of 1.7 percent as it seeks to smooth the volatility of rouble.

